org.robobrain.sdk.input
Class Multitouch

java.lang.Object
  org.robobrain.sdk.input.Multitouch

public class Multitouch
extends java.lang.Object

Simple holder class for Multitouch input. This class gets updated every time the user touches the screen. It can track up to 10 different pointers. (Fingers.)

Author:
James Johnson
